  "remarks": "\nAbdol Hossein Khosrow PANAH is an \n\"involved person\" under the Iran (Sanctions) Regulations 2023 because he is or has been involved in the commission of a serious human rights violation or abuse in Iran, including being responsible for, engaging in, providing support for and promoting violations of the right to freedom of expression, through his role as Secretary of the Supreme Council of the Cultural Revolution.",
